


# Install mosquitto

nstall a recent version of mosquitto library
follow instructions at http://mosquitto.org/download/

you can install repository or download directly, under debian:

wget http://repo.mosquitto.org/debian/mosquitto-repo.gpg.key
sudo apt-key add mosquitto-repo.gpg.key
cd /etc/apt/sources.list.d/
wget http://repo.mosquitto.org/debian/mosquitto-wheezy.list
apt-get update
apt-get install mosquitto-clients mosquitto python-mosquitto
